title: Qaleh-ye Mozaffari Rural District
text:
Qaleh-ye Mozaffari Rural District (Persian: دهستان قلعه مظفرئ‎) is a rural district (dehestan) in the Central District of Selseleh County, Lorestan Province, Iran. At the 2006 census, its population was 7,087, in 1,479 families.  The rural district has 39 villages.
